# Virtual Environment
.venv/

# Runtime State
# ``data/vor_request_count.json`` is intentionally NOT ignored — the
# VAO Start tier's 100/day quota counter must survive across cron runs
# (each GitHub-Actions runner is ephemeral, so an in-memory or
# runner-local counter would reset to 0 on every invocation and the
# script would silently re-spend the entire budget every 30 minutes).
# The Stammstrecke workflow commits this file alongside the cache and
# CSV ledger so the next run reads a coherent count.
data/*.lock
cache/**/*.lock
.hypothesis/
patch_lines.patch
